        "Web source 1"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.wildlifeconservation.blog/orange-lake-ny-guide"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The lake covers 400 acres, sits at 463 feet elevation, and reaches a maximum depth of 24 feet, offering ample boating and fishing.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        20,
        21
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 1",
